Caroline Paulus https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caroline_Paulus 0 Caroline Von Paulus (born March 1, 1959) is a French actress, fashion model and singer, better known by her stage name - Bambou. She was married to the French singer Serge Gainsbourg from 1981 until his death in 1991. Their son Lucien 'Lulu' Gainsbourg was born in 1986.
